    "body": "It may have been a case of premature modularization, yeah.\r\n\r\nI was wondering the same about ERC721, but I left it out of this issue because I think that distinction is because of the optional features in the standard. For ERC20 there's also that distinction between Standard and Detailed ERC20.\r\n\r\nI think it makes sense to provide the optional features separately.",
